          <h2 id="license-types">Two Different License Types</h2>
          <p>Niagara Falls has two distinct STR licenses under By-law 2021-57 (amended by 2025-033). Which one you need depends on whether you'll be living at the property:</p>

          <div class="comparison-table">
            <div class="comparison-header">
